lt's a simple life,
and l like it.

265
00:24:02,191 --> 00:24:03,233
Steve.

266
00:24:03,317 --> 00:24:07,487
l know who you are. l know
what you are, Vur Horsten.

267
00:24:09,198 --> 00:24:13,451
Who sent you? The Apocalypse
Monger? The Blood Barons?

268
00:24:13,536 --> 00:24:15,662
No... No one. l... No
one sent me. l just...

269
00:24:15,746 --> 00:24:18,123
l have these vampire books,
and l saw a painting of him

270
00:24:18,207 --> 00:24:20,083
with some girl in,
like, 1819.

271
