397
00:34:54,009 --> 00:34:59,013
Look, Octa bit my best friend,
Steve, and he's in the hospital,

398
00:34:59,431 --> 00:35:01,223
in a coma,
because of me.

399
00:35:01,308 --> 00:35:04,435
And l was wondering
if you had an antidote.

400
00:35:04,519 --> 00:35:05,853
l do.

401
00:35:05,937 --> 00:35:07,062
Thank you.

402
00:35:07,147 --> 00:35:09,690
