on some little psychopath?

404
00:35:13,361 --> 00:35:15,488
Please, l'm begging
you, okay?

405
00:35:15,572 --> 00:35:18,032
Look, l'm really sorry
l stole Octa.

406
00:35:18,700 --> 00:35:21,660
l don't know what came over
me. l never steal things.

