Mr. Tiny want?

415
00:35:40,222 --> 00:35:41,222
Mr. Tiny?

416
00:35:41,306 --> 00:35:43,015
The fat man
in the limousine!

417
00:35:44,893 --> 00:35:48,395
l don't know, something about
souls and... And destiny.

418
00:35:49,105 --> 00:35:50,147
