have much time left.

446
00:37:51,978 --> 00:37:56,523
Fine, l'll do it. To save my
friend, not for any other reason.

447
00:37:57,609 --> 00:37:59,151
So get the antidote.

448
00:37:59,235 --> 00:38:00,486
Right here.

449
00:38:02,697 --> 00:38:04,698
